title: Brady bounces back from sack attack - SouthCoastToday.com
text:
Chants of "Bra-dy" arose several times from a large New England contingent in Tom Brady's first visit to the $1.2 billion showplace of the Dallas Cowboys. First after a 1-yard plunge for his first rushing touchdown in almost three years, again after a long touchdown pass to Julian Edelman that helped seal the outcome and finally about 15 minutes after the end of the Patriots' 30-6 victory Sunday.
 SouthCoastToday.com.
